Build a Premium Luxury Perfume Website for SHIVRRA

Create a complete, production-ready luxury perfume website for the fragrance brand SHIVRRA.

This website should feel like a premium international fragrance house while remaining modern, elegant, cinematic, and highly interactive. The design should not feel like a generic Shopify perfume store. It should feel exclusive, luxurious, mysterious, and memorable.

The website will have only ONE product:

Product

Moon Oud
Luxury Eau De Parfum
50ml

Do not create separate Men and Women categories.

Instead create a single collection category called:

Unisex Collection

Moon Oud should be presented as a luxury unisex fragrance suitable for anyone who appreciates deep, rich, sophisticated scents.

Brand Identity

Brand Name

SHIVRRA

Brand Personality

Luxury

Elegant

Mysterious

Sophisticated

Modern

Premium

Timeless

Confident

Exclusive

The website should create the feeling of:

moonlight

oud wood

mystery

deep luxury

premium craftsmanship

signature scent culture

Typography

Use premium luxury typography.

Primary Font (Logo &amp; Headings)

Cormorant Garamond

Reason:

luxury fragrance feel

high-end editorial appearance

timeless elegance

works perfectly with the name SHIVRRA

Use it for:

logo

section headings

hero text

premium quotes

page titles

Secondary Font

Inter

Use for:

body text

buttons

navigation

product descriptions

Maintain strong typography hierarchy.

Large elegant headings.
Readable body text.

Color Palette

Use this exact luxury palette throughout the website.

Primary Colors

Deep Midnight Navy
#1F2A5A

Luxury Gold
#B88A2A

Charcoal Black
#1E1A1B

Soft Ivory
#F2F2F0

Smoky Grey
#B8BCC3

Visual Style

The entire website should feel like a luxury perfume advertisement.

Use:

dark backgrounds

cinematic lighting

luxury gold accents

glass reflections

subtle gradients

elegant shadows

premium spacing

luxury photography compositions

Avoid:

bright colors

playful design

clutter

generic ecommerce appearance

Product Photography

Generate and use AI-generated premium product advertisement photos throughout the website.

Create original luxury campaign visuals featuring:

Moon Oud perfume bottle with:

black stone

navy velvet

moonlight reflections

gold lighting

oud wood pieces

luxury marble

smoke effects

luxury gift box scenes

Images should look like professional perfume campaign photography and NOT obvious AI art.

Use multiple AI-generated hero images across the website.

Homepage

Create a highly interactive homepage.

Sections:

Announcement Bar

Luxury message:
&quot;Experience the Signature of Moon Oud&quot;

Navbar

Logo:
SHIVRRA

Navigation:

Home

Moon Oud

Our Story

Gifting

Corporate Gifting

Contact

Sticky navigation.

Transparent initially.
Luxury background after scrolling.

Hero Section

Large cinematic hero.

Headline:
&quot;Moon Oud&quot;

Subheadline:
&quot;Deep. Mysterious. Unforgettable.&quot;

Buttons:

Explore Fragrance

Shop Now

Use parallax effects.

Use luxury AI-generated campaign imagery.

Product Showcase Section

Large premium section showcasing Moon Oud.

Include:

Product bottle

Packaging

Features

Luxury presentation

Use animations while scrolling.

Fragrance Experience Section

Present Moon Oud as an experience.

Include:

Top Notes

Heart Notes

Base Notes

Display beautifully with luxury animations.

Why Moon Oud

Display luxury feature cards:

Long Lasting

Unisex

Premium Ingredients

Signature Scent

Elegant Packaging

Use hover animations.

Luxury Campaign Section

Full-width cinematic image section.

Large quote:

&quot;Some fragrances are worn.
Moon Oud is remembered.&quot;

Use smooth reveal animations.

Testimonials Section

Create elegant customer testimonials.

Use premium card design.

Newsletter Section

Luxury email signup section.

Moon Oud Product Page

Create a dedicated product page.

Include:

Large image gallery

Product information

Notes

Story

Quantity selector

Add to Cart button

Use smooth transitions.

Cart System

Create a fully functional cart UI.

When user clicks:

Checkout

DO NOT create payment gateway.

Instead redirect user to:

https://instagram.com/shivrra

Display button text:

&quot;Continue Purchase on Instagram&quot;

This should be the final checkout action.

Gifting Page

Create complete page design.

Use luxury visuals.

But display:

COMING SOON

Use:
Cormorant Garamond

Large gold typography.

Luxury background.

Animated reveal effect.

Corporate Gifting Page

Create luxury corporate gifting page.

Display:

COMING SOON

Use:
Cormorant Garamond

Large elegant typography.

Premium dark background.

Gold accents.

Luxury animation effects.

Our Story Page

Create a deep emotional luxury story.

Founder Story:

Write a sophisticated brand story.

Example direction:

SHIVRRA was born from the belief that fragrance is more than scent—it is memory, identity, and presence.

The founder spent years fascinated by how a single fragrance could transport someone back to a forgotten moment, a distant place, or a cherished memory. Moon Oud became the embodiment of that philosophy: a fragrance crafted not merely to be worn, but to leave an impression that lingers long after the moment has passed.

Inspired by quiet moonlit nights, timeless elegance, and the richness of oud, SHIVRRA was created for individuals who seek depth over noise and presence over attention.

Every bottle represents craftsmanship, emotion, and the pursuit of creating a signature scent that becomes part of a person&#39;s story.

Make this page emotional, cinematic, and premium.

Include:

timeline animations

image transitions

parallax effects

Contact Page

Create elegant contact page.

Include:

Email

Instagram

Inquiry Form

Luxury styling.

Pages NOT Required

Do NOT create:

Shipping Page

Returns Page

Track Order Page

Remove all references to them.

Keep navigation clean.

Animations

Use premium animations throughout the website.

Include:

Scroll reveal

Fade-up sections

Text reveal animations

Smooth page transitions

Image zoom effects

Luxury hover effects

Floating product motion

Mouse-follow glow effect

Subtle parallax

Framer Motion animations

Animations should feel premium, not excessive.

Mobile Optimization

The website MUST be mobile-first.

Requirements:

Fully responsive

Perfect on Android devices

Perfect on iPhone devices

Fast loading

Smooth scrolling

Touch-friendly buttons

Optimized images

Responsive typography

Every section must look premium on mobile.

Security Requirements

Build using modern secure web standards.

Implement:

HTTPS-ready architecture

Secure routing

Form validation

Input sanitization

XSS protection

CSRF protection where applicable

Secure state handling

No exposed secrets

No hardcoded credentials

Safe external linking

Performance optimization

The website should follow modern security best practices.

Final Goal

Create a visually stunning luxury perfume website for SHIVRRA that feels comparable to premium fragrance brands.

The website should focus entirely on:

Moon Oud

and establish SHIVRRA as a premium luxury fragrance house through exceptional design, typography, storytelling, animations, imagery, and user experience.

Every page should feel elegant, mysterious, immersive, and unforgettable."><button type="button" data-button="" data-icon-only="" aria-label="Edit message" class="btn-primitive relative isolate box-border inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap font-normal select-none disabled:opacity-50 gap-0.5 px-[9px] py-1 text-sm rounded-2 [&amp;_svg[data-default-size]]:size-4 !p-0 h-7 w-7" id="base-ui-_r_7p_" style="color: var(--fg-primary); background: transparent;"><span data-fx-layer="interaction" aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 rounded-[inherit] will-change-opacity transition-opacity duration-150 group-hover:duration-0 group-active:duration-0 z-0 [@media(hover:none)]:hidden opacity-[var(--_resting)] dark:opacity-[var(--_dark-resting)] can-hover:[[data-button]:hover_&amp;]:opacity-[var(--_hover)] dark:can-hover:[[data-button]:hover_&amp;]:opacity-[var(--_dark-hover)] [[data-button]:active_&amp;]:opacity-[var(--_pressed)] dark:[[data-button]:active_&amp;]:opacity-[var(--_dark-pressed)] [[data-button][aria-disabled=&#39;true&#39;]_&amp;]:opacity-[var(--_resting)] dark:[[data-button][aria-disabled=&#39;true&#39;]_&amp;]:opacity-[var(--_dark-resting)]" style="background-color: light-dark(oklch(0 0 0), oklch(1 0 0)); --_resting: 0; --_hover: 0.08; --_pressed: 0.1; --_dark-resting: 0; --_dark-hover: 0.12; --_dark-pressed: 0.16;"></span><span data-button-content="true" class="relative z-30 inline-flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center gap-0.5"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" class="shrink-0 size-5" aria-hidden="true" data-default-size="" data-button-icon=""><path d="M13.4697 5.46933C14.8672 4.07207 17.1328 4.07207 18.5303 5.46933C19.9277 6.86675 19.9276 9.1324 18.5303 10.5299L8.82324 20.2369C8.49509 20.5651 8.05001 20.7496 7.58594 20.7496H5C4.0335 20.7496 3.25 19.9661 3.25 18.9996V16.4137C3.25012 15.9497 3.43461 15.5044 3.7627 15.1764L13.4697 5.46933ZM